        {
            "date": "2011-06-02 15:29:22", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "Re: Can't maximise evolution\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "I verified this under a freshly-installed Natty (11.04) system.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "This happens because, using french language (as the original reporter), the minimum dimensions for the default Evolution window are 1029x414.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " Thus, when asked to \"maximize\" (i.e.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " setting width to 1024), Evolution plainly refuses because it knows that its child widgets won't fit.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "Of course, this involves two factors: width of the actual screen (that's why it's mostly prevalent on netbooks with narrower screens) and minimum width of the Evolution window, which mostly depends on language being used;", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " these kinds of problems don't usually show themselves in english because it happens to be a \"narrow\" language, so to speak.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "However, the problem can be reproduced in english as well, by using, for instance, a virtual machine with screen dimensions below 930x414 (the minimum size for the Evolution window in english), or perhaps by setting resolution to 800x600 or 640x480.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "This behavior happens even using the Classic session.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Steps to reproduce:\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "1- Install Natty, selecting the English language.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "2- Set the screen to a resolutionwith a width  lower than 930 pixels (800x600 works).\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "3- Start Evolution, create a possibly dummy configuration.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "4- Once the main Evolution window is on-screen, press the Maximize button\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Additionally, to validate using the original reporter's configuration (french):\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "5- sudo apt-get install language-pack-gnome-fr\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "6- Set the screen to a resolution with a width lower than 1029 pixels (1024x600, typical netbook resolution, works).\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "7- Start Evolution doing:\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "     LANG=\"fr_FR.UTF-8\" LANGUAGE=fr_FR  evolution\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "8- Maximize the Evolution window\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
